fields.headline: England Test squad
fields.bodyText: Test team to face India at The Oval, starting on Thursday Vaughan (Yorkshire, capt) Age 32 Tests 69, Strauss (Middlesex) 30 42, Cook (Essex) 22 20, Pietersen (Hampshire) 27 29, Collingwood (Durham) 31 26, Bell (Warwickshire) 25 29, Prior (Sussex, wkt) 25 6, Sidebottom (Nottinghamshire) 29 6, Tremlett (Hampshire) 25 2, Panesar (Northamptonshire) 25 19, Anderson (Lancashire) 25 18, Broad (Leicestershire) 21 0.
